snippet.textDisplay: “Warfaze was one of my favorite bands while growing up in the 90s in Bangladesh. We moved to California in 1992, so I never had the chance to see them perform in Bangladesh. However, there’s a rumor that they’ll be coming to California this October. I really hope it’s true. They’ve only gotten better over the years. Their performance of ‘Obak Bhalobasha’ on Coke Studio Bangla was amazing!”
